


to set user name for current repository to niharika

--- git config user.name "niharika"
to stage all new, modified, and deleted files

--- git add -A
to check the compact version of the status for repository

--- git status --short
commit the updated files directly skipping the staging area

--- git commit -a -m "commit message"
create, and move  to new branch with the name hello-you

--- git checkout -b hello-you
